item.title: 【Instrumentals / Karaoke (lossless)】PACK - Depeche Mode - Instrumentals [WAV/FLAC]
item.description:
So uhhh.... Hello again!

This time, let me show something i've been working on for the past few weeks. And that something is a pack, which consists of a Instrumental version of practically every Depeche Mode track. Most of these were made using Demucs (and most of these A.I. ones also used Audacity in order to tweak these instrumentals), but some of these come from either semi-official compilations, or even from promo CD's!.

Also an explanation on why some of them are in FLAC, and some of them are in WAV:
WAV - Fanmade via Demucs and Audacity.
FLAC - Either it was already an instrumental track, or it's a Semiofficial file, or it's an official instrumental from a promo CD

item.title: 【Cinema Center】MOVIE - Magic Mike (1080p) (BluRay) (x265) (2012) [PeterChaser]
item.description:
Plot: When your life is a fantasy, how do you deal with reality? As a male stripper, Magic Mike has everything he could ever want parties that last all night, hot girls and superfluous money. He takes a younger performer under his wing, teaching him the ropes on how to be the best. As he keeps at the top of the game in the clubs, Mike struggles with trying to develop a relationship with a girl he really likes. Will he have to choose between his dream world and real life? The dramatic comedy screenplay was inspired by Tatum's work as a 19-year-old stripper before he made it in Hollywood.
Cast: Channing Tatum, Alex Pettyfer, Matthew McConaughey, Cody Horn, Olivia Munn, Matt Bomer, Riley Keough, Joe Manganiello, Kevin Nash, Adam Rodriguez, Gabriel Iglesias
Director: Steven Soderbergh
Writer: Reid Carolin
